	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>tepples</b> [ Sun Jun 17, 2007 5:45 pm ]</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The relevant RAM location:
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">GameTimerCtrlTimer&nbsp; &nbsp; = $0787</div><br /><br />The code that writes a value to it:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">ResGTCtrl: lda #$18&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;;reset game timer control<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;sta GameTimerCtrlTimer</div>
<br />So put a watch on $0787 to find code like this.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


